> 0,\nand arbitrary a in R. If f in C^{0,l}_a then D^2 u in C^{0,l}_a.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 16 Oct 2015 16:07:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-10-19"}
