ley and ResearchGate. This third BIR workshop addresses explicitly\nboth scholarly and industrial researchers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 17 Oct 2015 11:51:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 18 Dec 2015 04:51:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-12-21"}
